ommendation":"none","all_time_high":14.46,"all_time_low":1.53,"long_business_summary":"Nivaka Fashions Limited engages in the manufacturing, trading, and sale of ethnic wear products for men and women in India and internationally. It provides sarees, lehengas, kurtis, suits, and gowns for women; kurtas, sherwanis, jackets, and kurta pyjamas for men; ethnic wear for children; and various jewelry products. The company also offers home d\u00e9cor products comprising bedsheets, tabletops, wall arts, dewan sets, home furnishings, and handicraft category products; and engages in textile trading activities. It provides tunic, western wear, western top, dresses, cord-sets, night suits, and indo western wear products. It sells its products through online channels under the Ninecolours West, Ninecolours Quirk, and Ninecolours Luxe brand names. The company was formerly known as B.T. Syndicate Limited and changed its name to Nivaka Fashions Limited in February 2020. Nivaka Fashions Limited was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Thane, India."}}